org.stanwood.media.store.mp4
Class AtomicParsley

java.lang.Object
  org.stanwood.media.util.AbstractExecutable
      org.stanwood.media.store.mp4.AtomicParsley

public class AtomicParsley
extends AbstractExecutable

This class is a wrapper the the atomic parsley application "http://atomicparsley.sourceforge.net/" It is used to store and retrieve atoms to a MP4 file.
